WEBVTT

00:00:00.950 --> 00:00:06.000
For the client review Ryan takes the demo.
He's strongest in the room.

00:00:06.599 --> 00:00:10.000
Priya, I need you on reporting
cleanup and the legacy bugs.

00:00:10.350 --> 00:00:15.000
Again? I've handled the
cleanup for the last three cycles.

00:00:15.150 --> 00:00:18.000
Ryan hasn't touched a bug report in months.

00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:21.000
Ryan's better suited for the
high pressure presentation.

00:00:23.250 --> 00:00:25.000
Let's not make this a thing Priya.